#: hardware.xml:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "IOP32x"
msgstr "IOP32x"

#. Tag: para
#: hardware.xml:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Intel's I/O Processor (IOP) line is found in a number of products related to "
"data storage and processing. &debian; currently supports the IOP32x "
"platform, featuring the IOP 80219 and 32x chips commonly found in Network "
"Attached Storage (NAS) devices. &debian; explicitly supports two such "
"devices: the <ulink url=\"&url-arm-cyrius-glantank;\">GLAN Tank</ulink> from "
"IO-Data and the <ulink url=\"&url-arm-cyrius-n2100;\">Thecus N2100</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Intel I/O Processor (IOP) 产品线可以在一些数据存储和处理的产品中找到。"
"&debian; 当前支持 IOP32x 平台，IOP 80219 和 32x 芯片通常在 Network Attached "
"Storage (NAS) 设备上找到。&debian; 明确支持两种设备：IO-Data 的 <ulink url="
"\"&url-arm-cyrius-glantank;\">GLAN Tank</ulink> 和 <ulink url=\"&url-arm-"
"cyrius-n2100;\">Thecus N2100</ulink>。"

